Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.32,0:00:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Burst into bloom - Red Crown!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.58,0:00:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you don't think that's\Nsufficient to deal with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you show yourself already?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:00:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Silas Norman...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.19,0:02:36.24,ArcName,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unshackled
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.77,0:02:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed that you realized\NI was the true perpetrator.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.61,0:02:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that slip of\Nthe tongue of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.41,0:02:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I don't know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.83,0:02:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, in the Business Area, this is\Nwhat you said in trying to stop Lester.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Waiting for a chance to duel...\Nyou'd never do anything cowardly like that!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what if I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:02:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing the media reported was\Nthat I'd repulsed my attackers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There was no report of my\Nhaving dueled Sasamiya that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't have been so sure about that\Nunless you actually saw it happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.69,0:03:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or else you'd been told of the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, it could only have been\Nthe perpetrator, and those in league with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well... How careless of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So in other words, Amagiri deliberately\Nprovoked Lester yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.95,0:03:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's the kind of guy who can\Nexpress himself without words.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, I see that I made\Nthe right call in targeting him instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's such a hindrance\Nwhen it comes to targeting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You came here just to stop me from\Ndoing that very thing, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.06,0:03:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, why don't we strike a deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My condition is that you withdraw\Nfrom the Phoenix Festa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:04:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All I have to do is annihilate you\Nright here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is what you just said true, Silas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lester!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.09,0:04:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I've been waiting for you, Lester.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I came rushing over when I heard\Nthat Julis had accepted my duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the one who attacked Julis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was hired by some academy or other,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to attack all the frontrunners\Nfor the Phoenix Festa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you've sold out\Nyour fellow students?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fellow students?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All of us here in Asterisk\Nare mutual enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're only here to target others, and be targeted,\Nto fulfill our own desires, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That being the case, wouldn't it be wiser\Nto make money by taking advantage of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.75,0:05:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna ask you before\NI kick the crap outta you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you make a point of\Nsummoning me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to have you assume the role of\Nthe man behind all those attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You two dueled each other, and\Nyou both fell, like the best of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.27,0:05:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd call that a likely\Nscenario, wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So those are the comrades\Nyou're so proud of?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't be absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These are my precious,\Nprecious little dolls!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Puppets?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you wouldn't lump them in\Nwith something so crude.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's absolutely nothing\Nmechanical about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:06:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so that's where\Nyour true talent lies, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.53,0:06:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.95,0:06:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Blast Nemea!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lester!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, please sit tight right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've raised their heat\Nthreshold just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're only capable of\Ndirty tricks like sucker-punching.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, you're in better\Nshape than I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many of these\Nwooden puppets you sic on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many I sic on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, as you wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be happy to take you on\Nwith 128 of these!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I like that look on your face!\NNow then... farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lester!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Silas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Burst into bloom - Antirrhinum majus!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I must say, that's quite impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But at the end of the day,\Nyou're still outnumbered!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your skills are certainly prodigious,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but the way they conceal\Nyour own view as well is a real flaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've discovered something myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.93,0:08:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And what would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.43,0:08:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That it's Allekant that's\Npulling your strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No school is capable of mass-producing the kind of\Narmor that can withstand our attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,except for Allekant!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.41,0:08:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Quite perceptive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:09:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm afraid there's no way\NI can afford to let you go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning to enjoy myself\Nby inflicting pain on you a bit longer,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I've changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.09,0:09:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll just get this over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I got held up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.61,0:09:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You... What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to save you, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:10:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is my problem, and\Nit has nothing to do with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So why would you go out of\Nyour way to venture into danger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.52,0:10:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Julis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You told me that you were fighting\Nof your own free will - for yourself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That you're protecting\Nthe kids in that orphanage
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.15,0:10:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,just because that's what you want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.45,0:10:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then, who's going to\Nprotect you, Julis?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who's... going to...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You see, Julis...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been searching for it all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.63,0:10:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What it is that I'm capable of,\Nwhat it is that I'm supposed to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But now that I've met you\Nhere, I finally get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.13,0:10:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, if there's something I want to do,\Nand if I have what it takes to do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's what I'm supposed to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What you're supposed to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be there for you, Julis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.28,0:10:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You moron! Where do you\Nget off saying such things?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done chatting?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Ayato Amagiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So was that the power of\Nthe Ser Veresta?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.71,0:11:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I see it's a bit of a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That said, although your surprise attack\Njust now seems to have worked out,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,just what do you hope to accomplish\Nagainst over 100 of my dolls?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up. You're the one who's\Nonly capable of surprise attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.27,0:11:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Silas Norman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.73,0:11:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How rude of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, would you care to test me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the sword inside me, I shall\Nbreak out of this starry prison,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and release my savage force!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.37,0:12:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,P-Put me down this instant!\NI have no intention of hindering you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but could you put up\Nwith this just a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.43,0:12:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This time I'm going to go all-out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the essence of\Nmy Merciless Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try fending them off if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The most puppets you can move\Nindividually is up to six types, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.77,0:13:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And there are sixteen puppets\Nwho execute a certain pattern of moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.81,0:13:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The rest only take\Nthe simplest of actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Six types, sixteen pieces...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.53,0:13:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're evoking chess?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.49,0:13:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll demolish you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.62,0:13:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I swear I'll demolish you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A sword that can't be\Nblocked, no matter what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.81,0:14:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Game over, Silas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! I've still got\Nmy secret technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, my queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get rid of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.93,0:14:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ripping apart the five viscera\Nand severing the four limbs...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amagiri Shinmei-style, Second Sword...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nine-fanged Sword!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You sure don't know when to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.71,0:15:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Julis. I'm gonna go after him,\Nso would you mind waiting here a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.05,0:15:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind, but will you make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.01,0:15:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case... it's my turn, then. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.48,0:15:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before... I'm not\Ngoing to drag you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.19,0:15:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Burst into bloom - Strelitzia!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! I'll pilot you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This time, make sure\Nyou bash that coward's face in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,not exactly what\Na princess would say, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Checkmate...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Silas Norman!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.18,0:16:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since Silas is a Genestella himself,\NI'm sure this won't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.65,0:16:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And Claudia and the others\Nshould be waiting down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.07,0:16:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So how about we leave\Nthe rest to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.67,0:16:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's an awesome view, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.71,0:16:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly is a glorious sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:16:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:17:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.07,0:17:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Stay with me, Ayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry, Ayato.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big Sister?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With these circular shackles,\NI imprison your savage force.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.23,0:17:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}B-Big Sister...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.27,0:17:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Remember what I told you before?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That I'd be the one to protect you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.32,0:17:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.86,0:17:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I told you that I'd protect you, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.58,0:18:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Goodbye, Ayato.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I love you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.63,0:18:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you've finally come to!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really, for a while there\NI didn't know what to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.39,0:18:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I did pass out, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.36,0:18:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've already contacted Claudia,\Nand they'll be coming to get us soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N-No need to thank me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're the one who saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.25,0:18:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Don't move around like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.38,0:18:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M-My bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.71,0:18:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N-Never mind that,\Njust lie still, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.22,0:19:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm telling you\Nit's all right, so it's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get that through your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.76,0:19:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That power that's restraining you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.73,0:19:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it cast by?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.86,0:19:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.45,0:19:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.58,0:19:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She had Imprisonment Power.\NThe power to forcibly bind all things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.79,0:19:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning that those were\Nyour true powers, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I guess you could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?\NSuch a vague answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can only use them for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.35,0:19:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time they've lasted\Nfor more than five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.56,0:19:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And to top it all off,\Nlook at the state I'm left in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.57,0:19:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did your sister do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'd ask her myself if I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As it is, she went\Nmissing five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.62,0:20:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. I'm sure that\Nmy sister had her reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm sure there must be\Nsome kind of point to all this, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay if I ask you\None more question?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have you already decided on your\Ntag partner for the Phoenix Festa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.72,0:20:21.51,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.97,0:20:23.47,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'd fit the bill?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:24.97,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:29.43,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a man of integrity, and\Nmy mind is just average-quick,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:34.02,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and you'll have to give me a pass\Non the strong will, noble spirit thing, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:36.98,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate your offer,\Nbut don't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.69,0:20:41.61,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the Festa level, your normal\Npowers just won't translate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:46.91,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you wouldn't want to end up this way after\Nunsealing your powers after every match.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.16,0:20:49.41,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm totally cool with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:52.83,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:55.42,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,what I'm supposed to do right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:58.76,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis, it's to be there for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.84,0:21:02.22,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N-No... But the thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:04.64,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These things should be handled more...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.01,0:21:06.55,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, are you embarrassed?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.55,0:21:07.97,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is bright red!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.97,0:21:09.85,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Of course I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:11.39,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway, d-don't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.39,0:21:13.02,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,J-Julis!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.98,0:21:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.86,0:21:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, you really are a strange one...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.41,0:21:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.93,0:21:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.89,0:21:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you couldn't have been ignorant of\Nthis one's power, could you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.45,0:22:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man, don't tell me\Nyou actually wasted him, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.67,0:22:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No worries, he's not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.05,0:22:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He can still be of some use, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.84,0:22:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So instead of going public with this incident\Nand using it as a diplomatic chip,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.14,0:22:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you're going to take care of it internally,\Nand make Allekant owe us, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.35,0:22:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to leave this to\Nthe discretion of you Shadow Stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.39,0:22:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please be sure to get\Nsome information out of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.02,0:22:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can count on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.23,0:22:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's our job.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.65,0:22:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So? How did it go with those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.40,0:22:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to have gone well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.74,0:22:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you don't look\Ntoo happy, considering.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.83,0:22:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really? I wouldn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.41,0:22:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.00,0:23:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've acquired enough data,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.34,0:23:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and they even did a better job\Nwith those bonus sneak attacks
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.59,0:23:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,on the frontrunners\Nthan I'd dared to hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.18,0:23:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well, but maybe that was only because\Nmy little puppets were so competent?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.18,0:23:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, these semi-intelligent beings are\Nso easy to handle, it's a godsend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.61,0:23:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's my Ayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.61,0:23:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your relationship with Julis\Nmakes me somewhat jealous,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.62,0:23:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but it's for the Phoenix Festa.\NI shall endure it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.66,0:23:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now if only our school's Rank #1...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:40.04,Next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 5 - Lightning Blade Speed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.66,0:23:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,if only she would agree to compete...
